default.
Build-from-source during deployment is fragile and slow. Each deploy compiles
OpenClaw from the pinned git ref using pnpm, which can take 5+ minutes and requires
2GB+ memory. GitHub GitHub A pre-built Docker image or build cache strategy would
dramatically improve deployment reliability and speed.
